
Lending Page

This repository contains the source code for the Easybank landing page project, developed using Sass, HTML, and CSS.

Project Overview

The project showcases a responsive landing page with modern design elements and a user-friendly interface.

Features

- Responsive design for both mobile and desktop views.
- Clean and organized code structure.
- Implemented styles using Sass for better maintainability.

Project Structure

- index.html: Main HTML file.
- style-guide.md: Contains style guidelines and design specifications.

How to Use

1. Clone the repository.
2. Open index.html in your web browser to view the landing page.

Live Demo

You can view a live demo of the project [here](https://yomarsanchez.github.io/easybank-landing-page).

Resources

- Challenge: [Frontend Mentor Challenge](https://www.frontendmentor.io/challenges/easybank-landing-page-WaUhkoDN)
